    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-05-18T09:16:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-05-18T09:16:00-05:00" n="934"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d934">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 635.119/470</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Argentina</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_SFJ1"
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">F. J. Stimson</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Buenos Aires</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-05-18T10:00:00-04:16">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 18, 1918, 10 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received 11.50 a.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your May 3, 4 p.m. I delivered the substance of these instructions to <persName
                        corresp="#p_NRS1">Naón</persName> and last night the Minister of Marine
                    informally <pb facs="0919" n="835" xml:id="pg_835"/> told me that the Argentine
                    Government would consider the explanation entirely satisfactory and the incident
                    closed.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_SFJ1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Stimson</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
